<style>
  .text-image-block_wrapp-text {
    width: calc(100% - 710px);
  }
  .text-image-block_wrapp-image {
    width: 660px;
    height: 560px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: 50% 50%;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 11px;
  }
  @media(max-width: 1450px) {
    .text-image-block_wrapp-image {
      width: 550px;
    }
    .text-image-block_wrapp-text {
        width: calc(100% - 600px);
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 1250px) {
    .text-image-block_wrapp {
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .text-image-block_wrapp-text {
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .text-image-block_wrapp-image {
        max-width: 600px;
        width: 100%;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 750px) {
    .text-image-block .rebranding_container {
      padding: 0;
    }
    .text-image-block_wrapp-text {
      padding: 0 15px;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .text-image-block_wrapp-text p {
      text-align: justify;
    }
    .text-image-block_wrapp-image {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: 400px;
      border-radius: 0;
    }
  }
</style>

<div class="rebranding_container">
  <div class="text-image-block_wrapp block-flex-wrap block-gap-50 block-flex-center-sb">
    <div class="text-image-block_wrapp-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <h3 class="h2-heading-ss w-100">
        Why   
        <span class="h2-heading-pp">
          Balenciaga luxury goods
        </span>
        are so desirable?
      </h3>
      <p class="body-text">
        Balenciaga luxury goods are highly coveted by fashion enthusiasts for their unique designs and exceptional quality. The brand is renowned for pushing the boundaries of fashion with its avant-garde designs and unconventional approach. 
        <br><br>
        Each Balenciaga item is crafted with the finest materials, ensuring that every piece is not only stylish but also durable. From the iconic Motorcycle bag to the latest runway pieces, Balenciaga’s creations are a testament to the brand’s commitment to excellence. 
        <br><br>
        This dedication to quality and innovation makes Balenciaga items highly sought after by collectors and fashion aficionados worldwide. Whether it’s Balenciaga handbags, shoes, or clothing, owning a piece from this illustrious brand means possessing a part of fashion history.
      </p>
    </div>
    <img class="text-image-block_wrapp-image" src="{{ "balenciaga_desirable.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Balenciaga luxury goods">
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
  {
    "name": "SEO Text & image",
    "class": "text-image-block rebranding-wider-section-bottom",
    "settings": []
  }
{% endschema %}